  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Build a Playground for Sick Children in Kenya</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Hospitalization is a stressful experience to all and more to children. Child Life Programs help children navigate hospitalization with minimal stress and anxiety. Play helps children respond better to treatment and so children heal faster and are discharged home sooner. Sally Test Paediatric Centre provides therapeutic play activities to sick children in a resource poor public hospital in Kenya. We serve approximate 300 children in a day both inpatient and outpatient</narrative>
  </description>
